<c.bg_transparent>Vou picar a mula!</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:55.065 --> 00:12:57.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Avise se quiser comprar saveiros usados!</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:04.909 --> 00:13:06.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mas que...</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:13:07.703 --> 00:13:10.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sem saída! Vamos nadar pra fugir!</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:13:10.122 --> 00:13:11.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Venha!</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:13:27.765 --> 00:13:29.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É por isso que alugo, não compro.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:13:51.705 --> 00:13:53.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bean. Veja.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:13:59.588 --> 00:14:01.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não sabia que era mateiro.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:14:01.966 --> 00:14:04.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não, só estou descontando nos cipós.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:14:06.345 --> 00:14:08.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estamos chegando.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:14:08.222 --> 00:14:10.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Por que diz isso?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Por causa dos ogros.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:14:17.398 --> 00:14:22.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Espere aí. Ogros têm medo de fogo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Medo mortal! O Wade falou.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:14:23.279 --> 00:14:25.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wade é um canalha mentiroso.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:14:25.364 --> 00:14:28.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eu juro, Bean, ele pegou tudo do livro.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Ele não...</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:14:31.662 --> 00:14:32.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bean, não.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:14:37.001 --> 00:14:38.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sou a princesa Tiabeanie!</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:14:38.836 --> 00:14:41.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Princesa do fogo mágico!</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:14:41.130 --> 00:14:44.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fogo! Viram a ponta do bastão?</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:14:45.509 --> 00:14:49.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entreguem os frutos!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Senão, fogo! Fogo assustador!</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:15:02.568 --> 00:15:04.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por favor, podem andar mais juntos?</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:15:06.322 --> 00:15:10.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ficou tudo na minha mão.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Sou o elfo mais corajoso desde o Bravo.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:15:10.951 --> 00:15:13.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Até ele arregar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>e "Bravo" ganhar outro significado:</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:15:13.871 --> 00:15:15.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>o elfo que aplaude.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:15:23.547 --> 00:15:27.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wade! Aqui! Sabia que viria nos salvar.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:16:13.180 --> 00:16:15.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A árvore do fruto lendário!</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:16:15.307 --> 00:16:19.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se o papai não mentiu sobre isso,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>vai ver não roubou minha poupança.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:16:22.064 --> 00:16:24.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como ousa roubar da Árvore do Fruto!</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:16:26.402 --> 00:16:29.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pegamos esse trepador</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tentando roubar os frutos sagrados.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:16:29.613 --> 00:16:32.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Primeiro, a atrevida, agora, o nanico?</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:16:32.282 --> 00:16:34.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Recheie o baixote com um frango</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pra rechear a garota,</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:16:34.743 --> 00:16:37.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>e vamos comer bem amanhã depois da igreja.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:16:40.666 --> 00:16:42.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É ele, pai!</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:16:42.376 --> 00:16:45.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ser ele que meu olho ser ele quem ele ser!</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:16:46.505 --> 00:16:49.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Júnior! Chega disso!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Brinque com o crânio dele amanhã.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:16:49.842 --> 00:16:50.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mãe.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:16:51.010 --> 00:16:54.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Passe os sete temperos sagrados</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>e o atire no calabouço.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:17:03.313 --> 00:17:05.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não se preocupe, Bean! Vou salvá-la!</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:17:05.899 --> 00:17:08.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não sou uma donzela em perigo.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:17:08.402 --> 00:17:10.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tecnicamente, eu sou, mas mesmo assim...</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:17:15.492 --> 00:17:19.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dedo na orelha? Que nojo!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Foi criado num chiqueiro?</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:17:20.164 --> 00:17:24.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não quero fazer isso.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Solte minha amiga, e vamos embora.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:17:27.171 --> 00:17:30.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Prepare-se, Elfo Malvado. Hora de brilhar.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:17:50.944 --> 00:17:51.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não!</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:17:54.656 --> 00:17:55.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Essa não!</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:18:12.341 --> 00:18:15.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vou ficar bem.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Só preciso me deitar um pouco.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:18:16.470 --> 00:18:17.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eita, Elfo.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:18:17.679 --> 00:18:19.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Você dá medo nessa fúria sanguinária.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:18:20.057 --> 00:18:21.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vamos sair daqui.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:18:21.266 --> 00:18:23.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não sem os malditos frutos.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:18:32.611 --> 00:18:34.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não me obrigue a fazer isto, Majestade.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:18:34.822 --> 00:18:37.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Só queremos os frutos.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Meu povo está morrendo.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:18:38.033 --> 00:18:39.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>De onde são, nanicos?</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:18:39.535 --> 00:18:42.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Terra dos Sonhos. Antes éramos...</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:18:44.414 --> 00:18:47.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ande, pegue os frutos!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Se for visto, terei de comê-lo.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:18:57.636 --> 00:18:59.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Calados. Venham comigo.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:19:03.892 --> 00:19:06.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esse bueiro velho leva ao rio.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:19:06.478 --> 00:19:08.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Você é bem legal para uma rainha.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:19:08.147 --> 00:19:10.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Valeu. Tome isto.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:19:13.443 --> 00:19:15.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Desculpe. Já comemos o corpo. Agora, vão.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:19:21.326 --> 00:19:22.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não pise nos ratos, Elfo.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:19:24.079 --> 00:19:25.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Elfo?</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:19:25.247 --> 00:19:30.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>É isso. O fim da melhor história</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que já contei: minha vida!</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:19:30.127 --> 00:19:33.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se vir o Elfo, pode dizer que eu o amo?</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:19:33.255 --> 00:19:34.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A mãe também o amava.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:19:35.048 --> 00:19:38.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Meus órgãos pararam. Adeus.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:19:42.556 --> 00:19:44.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Adeus, velho doido.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:19:44.850 --> 00:19:46.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Conseguimos! Trouxemos os frutos!</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:19:46.977 --> 00:19:49.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Tarde demais, mano. Ele se foi.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Não, pai!</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:19:52.941 --> 00:19:54.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por favor, pai.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:19:56.195 --> 00:19:57.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ele morreu, Elfo.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:19:57.571 --> 00:19:59.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ele logo estará com os siris.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:19:59.323 --> 00:20:00.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Podem me dar licença?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:20:07.372 --> 00:20:10.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pai, você foi um bom pai.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:20:10.584 --> 00:20:13.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mesmo com suas histórias longas, chatas,</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:20:13.503 --> 00:20:17.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>sem graça e, claramente, mentirosas,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>vou sentir saudade.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:20:19.009 --> 00:20:21.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não acredito que morreu.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:20:21.094 --> 00:20:23.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não morri, caramba!</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:20:23.430 --> 00:20:24.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pai, você está vivo!</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:20:24.806 --> 00:20:26.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Todos estamos vivos, caramba!</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:20:29.645 --> 00:20:33.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ouvi tudo que falou.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Sabe de uma coisa, Elfo?</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:20:33.148 --> 00:20:35.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que bom que roubei sua poupança.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:20:35.525 --> 00:20:36.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quê?</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:21:34.584 --> 00:21:36.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Legendas: Leandro Woyakoski</c.bg_transparent>

